I worked with Elina Lin, Chris Gebhart, Derek Remsburg, and Moonsoo Choi on this project and after some deliberation, we decided on a catapult, a design many other groups tried as well. Since it was to be fully automated after a ball is rolled in, we designed a trigger that locks due to friction.


