On Presentation Day, we demonstrated our catapult’s ability to knock over the soda can numerous times. You can see our final timed run in the Youtube video below. The final count was 15 cans, about 10 cans more compared to the next best-performing group. As a result, we ended up in 2nd place out of the entire class.


